title: George Kittle and Sanu: Trey Lance Has Insane Ceiling | I AM ATHLETE
description:

Season 3 | Episode 29
In Episode 29 of I Am Athlete, Brandon Marshall travels to Technogym's headquarters in Cesena, Italy and connects with San Francisco 49ers tight end George Kittle and wide receiver Mohamed Sanu. Watch as Kittle and Sanu discuss the 49er's quarterback battle between Jimmy Garoppolo and Trey Lance, the power of visualization and Kittle's 75 acre Golf course.

Kittle and Sanu also dive deeper into the their personal experience with Technogym. They discuss how Technogym is a leader in the industry and how their products are playing a big role in the future of training for them and other athletes.
